<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_cafcc3b10cbc.aspx"><b>北风</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsoncafcc3b10cbc">
北风其凉，雨雪其雱。惠而好我，携手同行。其虚其邪？既亟只且！<br />北风其喈，雨雪其霏。惠而好我，携手同归。其虚其邪？既亟只且！<br />莫赤匪狐，莫黑匪乌。惠而好我，携手同车。其虚其邪？既亟只且！
